metadata.name: Lords of Swing #1
metadata.description:
Step up to the tee and swing into golfing history with Lords of Swing by Birds of Condor. These digital collectibles have been created to immortalise 19 of the most iconic moments in golfing history, and connect golfers across the globe who are committed to bringing the flavour back to #GolfLife.
Owning a Lords of Swing grants you unprecedented access to the entire Birds of Condor ecosystem.
Art by Kentaro Yoshida.
